description: Professional architectural blueprint for a 2 Acres house with For my dream house in Coimbatore, I envision a modern and spacious layout that maximizes natural light and ventilation. The floor plan should include a large living room, 3-4 bedrooms with attached bathrooms, a separate dining area, and a kitchen with an island. I’d love an outdoor area for relaxation and entertainment, such as a patio or garden. The house should have ample storage space, including wardrobes and utility rooms. I prefer an open-plan design for the common areas and a functional yet aesthetically pleasing arrangement of rooms to ensure comfort and convenience.. Top-down 2D floor plan with precise measurements, clean lines, labeled rooms, doors, windows, and dimensions. Technical architectural drawing style with blue lines on white background.
